<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/10(Sat.)Taiwanese director wins big at film festival in France/Taiwan illustrator wins BolognaRagazzi Award (Pinn)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=522&amp;p=545#p545"><![CDATA[
7/10(Sat.)Taiwanese director wins big at film festival in France/Taiwan illustrator wins BolognaRagazzi Award (Host: Pinn)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">There is no on-site meeting during the pandemic of COVID-19.<br /><br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation, the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.</span><br /><br />Article 1:Taiwanese director wins big at film festival in France<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4217960">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4217960</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Question:<br />1. What kind of movies do you like most?<br />2. Will you pay money to see the movies winning  a good prize? <br /> 3. Do you like to see Taiwanese movies?<br /><br />Article 2:Taiwanese illustrator Animo Chen wins BolognaRagazzi Award<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.moc.gov.tw/en/en/information_196_129950.html">https://www.moc.gov.tw/en/en/informatio ... 29950.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question:<br />1. Do you like illustration films? <br />2. Which kind of illustration films do you like?<br />3. Will you allow your children to be an illustrator?<br /><br /><span style="color: #0000FF">P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~</span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Jul 08, 2021 9:15 am</p><hr />
